=============================================================
|ID|OPERATOR                 |NAME    |EST.ROWS|EST.TIME(us)|
-------------------------------------------------------------
|0 |PX COORDINATOR           |        |1       |10          |
|1 |└─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR     |:EX10000|1       |10          |
|2 |  └─PX PARTITION ITERATOR|        |1       |9           |
|3 |    └─TABLE FULL SCAN    |p2      |1       |9           |
=============================================================
